---
<section class="spotlight">
  <div class="spotlight-image">
    <img src="/images/posts/07.jpg" alt="Spicy Chicken Ramen" />
  </div>
  <div class="spotlight-text">
    <span class="badge-label">viral recipe!</span>
    <h2>Spicy Chicken Ramen</h2>
    <p>A bold, comforting noodle soup made with a savory broth, tender chicken, and classic ramen toppings. Ready in 30 minutes and bursting with flavor.</p>
    <a href="/recipes/spicy-chicken-ramen" class="cta-btn">Get the recipe →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .spotlight {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    min-height: 480px;
    background: #f5ede8;
  }
  .spotlight-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  .spotlight-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 60px 48px;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .badge-label {
    font-family: 'Dancing Script', 'Brush Script MT', cursive;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: #c0582a;
  }
  .spotlight-text h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin: 0;
    color: #2a2a2a;
  }
  .spotlight-text p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 400px;
    color: #555;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 13px 26px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    width: fit-content;
    background: #c0582a;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .cta-btn:hover {
    background: #a0461e;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .spotlight {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .spotlight-image img {
      max-height: 320px;
    }
    .spotlight-text {
      padding: 40px 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
